HEADWORD: Rantipole
<hw>Rant"i*pole</hw> <pr>(r⟦acr⟧nt"⟦icr⟧*p⟦omac⟧l)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Ranty</ets> + <ets>pole</ets>, <ets>poll</ets>, head.]</ety>
<def>A wild, romping young person.</def> <mark>[Low]</mark>
<rj><au>Marryat.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
