<p><ent>Rantipole</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Rantipole
<hw>Rant"i*pole</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Wild; roving; rakish.</def>
<mark>[Low]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Rantipole</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 3 ====
HEADWORD: Rantipole
<hw>Rant"i*pole</hw>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <def>To act like a
rantipole.</def> <mark>[Low]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>She used to <qex>rantipole</qex> about the house.</q>
<rj><qau>Arbuthnot.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Rantism</ent>⟦br⟧
